data.description: Beautiful spacious home located in the highly sought after Broken Arrow "Bricktown" neighborhood. This home is 4 bedrooms and 3 full bathrooms. Up the stairs you will find a wonderful game room along with another bedroom and bathroom making it perfect for children or guests. All new carpet throughout. Two living areas, hobby room, vaulted ceilings, cute kitchen with build in seating in the kitchen nook. Huge back patio and firepit for entertaining. Ring door bell and security cameras stay with the home. Within minutes to plenty of shopping and restaurants.
